<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Spring-Context on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/spring-context/</link><description>Recent content in Spring-Context on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/spring-context/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>BeanCreationException in AOP proxy</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/frameworks/spring/spring-aop-error/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/frameworks/spring/spring-aop-error/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;This error occurs when Spring fails to create an AOP proxy for a bean, typically due to circular dependencies, missing aspect definitions, or incompatible proxy modes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Circular dependency involving proxied beans&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;@Aspect&lt;/code&gt; class has injection issues&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Final methods cannot be proxied (CGLIB limitation)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proxy mode mismatch (JDK vs CGLIB)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bean initialization fails before proxy is created&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Enable CGLIB proxying if using final methods:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-java" data-lang="java"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;@EnableAspectJAutoProxy&lt;/span&gt;(proxyTargetClass &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;@Configuration&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;class&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;AopConfig&lt;/span&gt; { }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="2"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Break circular dependencies:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-java" data-lang="java"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;@Service&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;class&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;OrderService&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;private&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;final&lt;/span&gt; Lazy&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;OrderValidator&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; validator;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;OrderService&lt;/span&gt;(Lazy&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;OrderValidator&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; validator) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;this&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;validator&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; validator; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Breaks the circular dependency&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="3"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Verify aspect configuration:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-java" data-lang="java"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;@Aspect&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;@Component&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;class&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;LoggingAspect&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;@Around&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;execution(* com.example.service.*.*(..))&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; Object &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;logMethodCall&lt;/span&gt;(ProceedingJoinPoint joinPoint) &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;throws&lt;/span&gt; Throwable {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;long&lt;/span&gt; start &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; System.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;currentTimeMillis&lt;/span&gt;();
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; Object result &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; joinPoint.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;proceed&lt;/span&gt;();
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;long&lt;/span&gt; duration &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; System.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;currentTimeMillis&lt;/span&gt;() &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt; start;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; log.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;info&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Method {} took {}ms&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, joinPoint.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;getSignature&lt;/span&gt;(), duration);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; result;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-java" data-lang="java"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;@Service&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;class&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;ServiceA&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;@Autowired&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;private&lt;/span&gt; ServiceB b;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;@Service&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;class&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;ServiceB&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;@Autowired&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;private&lt;/span&gt; ServiceA a;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// BeanCreationException: Requested bean could not be created — circular reference&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/frameworks/spring/spring-bean-not-found/"&gt;Bean not found&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/frameworks/spring/spring-validation-error/"&gt;Validation error&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>No qualifying bean of type 'X'</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/frameworks/spring/bean-not-found/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/frameworks/spring/bean-not-found/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;This error occurs when Spring&amp;rsquo;s application context cannot locate a bean that matches the type required for injection. It typically surfaces at startup when a &lt;code&gt;@Autowired&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;@Inject&lt;/code&gt;, or constructor injection target has no matching bean definition.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The class is not annotated with &lt;code&gt;@Component&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;@Service&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;@Repository&lt;/code&gt;, or &lt;code&gt;@Configuration&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The class is in a package not covered by &lt;code&gt;@ComponentScan&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Multiple beans of the same type exist and no &lt;code&gt;@Primary&lt;/code&gt; or &lt;code&gt;@Qualifier&lt;/code&gt; is specified&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The bean is conditionally created (&lt;code&gt;@ConditionalOnProperty&lt;/code&gt;) and the condition is not met&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ensure the class is properly annotated and within the component scan path:&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>NoSuchBeanDefinitionException - bean not found</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/frameworks/spring/spring-bean-not-found/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/frameworks/spring/spring-bean-not-found/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;This error occurs when Spring&amp;rsquo;s application context cannot find a bean matching the type required for dependency injection. It typically surfaces at startup when &lt;code&gt;@Autowired&lt;/code&gt; or constructor injection targets have no matching bean definition.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Class is not annotated with &lt;code&gt;@Component&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;@Service&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;@Repository&lt;/code&gt;, or &lt;code&gt;@Configuration&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bean is in a package not covered by &lt;code&gt;@ComponentScan&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Multiple beans of the same type exist without &lt;code&gt;@Primary&lt;/code&gt; or &lt;code&gt;@Qualifier&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bean is conditionally created via &lt;code&gt;@ConditionalOnProperty&lt;/code&gt; and the condition is not met&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Interface has no concrete implementation registered as a bean&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Annotate the class properly:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-java" data-lang="java"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;@Service&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;class&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;OrderService&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Spring will find this bean&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="2"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Qualify injection when multiple beans exist:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-java" data-lang="java"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;@Autowired&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;@Qualifier&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;stripePaymentService&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;private&lt;/span&gt; PaymentService paymentService;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="3"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Expand component scan if the bean is in a sub-package:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-java" data-lang="java"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;@SpringBootApplication&lt;/span&gt;(scanClasses &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; AppConfig.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;class&lt;/span&gt;,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; com.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;other&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;package&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;ModuleConfig&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;class&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;})
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;class&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Application&lt;/span&gt; { }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="4"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use &lt;code&gt;@Primary&lt;/code&gt; to mark the default bean:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-java" data-lang="java"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;@Service&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;@Primary&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;class&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;DefaultPaymentService&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;implements&lt;/span&gt; PaymentService { }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-java" data-lang="java"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;@RestController&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;class&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;UserController&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;@Autowired&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;private&lt;/span&gt; UserService userService; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// No @Service annotation&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// NoSuchBeanDefinitionException: No qualifying bean of type &amp;#39;com.example.UserService&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/frameworks/spring/validation-error/"&gt;Validation error&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=""&gt;AOP error&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>